findings.suggestion:
Add JSDoc to both interfaces and annotate conditionally-required fields. Example:
/** Persisted MCP server configuration. */
export interface McpServerConfig {
  /** Unique identifier (nanoid). */
  id: string
  /** Required when transport is 'stdio'. The executable to spawn. */
  command?: string
  /** Required when transport is 'sse' or 'http'. The server endpoint URL. */
  url?: string
}
